Package: clevo-control-center
Version: 0.1.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Clevo Control Center Contributors <qcqcqc@zust.online>
Depends: libc6, zenity | kdialog
Recommends: pkexec, make, linux-headers-amd64
Homepage: https://github.com/pqcqaq/clevo-control-center-linux
Provides: clevo-keyboard-led
Conflicts: clevo-keyboard-led
Replaces: clevo-keyboard-led
Description: Clevo/BlueSky control center for Linux
 Rust GUI, background lighting service, and restricted DCHU control CLI for
 compatible Clevo-family laptops. The package includes the kernel module
 source and tries to build it for the running kernel when headers are present.
